f=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-theme-shops/\">33 Best WordPress Theme Shops to Buy the Perfect Theme</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46303:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress theme shops to buy an eye-catching theme for your website?</p>\n<p>There are endless WordPress theme shops in the marketplace offering different types of layouts and designs. But, if you&#8217;re looking for a theme that truly fits your site like a glove, the most important factors to consider when exploring a theme company include niche, features, customization options, and flexibility.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best WordPress theme shops to buy the perfect theme for your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress/\" title=\"StudioPress\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. StudioPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress/\" title=\"StudioPress\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/studiopress.jpg\" alt=\"StudioPress\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231999\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/studiopress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/studiopress-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/studiopress-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>StudioPress is a popular WordPress theme shop with many beautiful premium themes. All of their themes ship with the Genesis framework which makes them powerful and flexible in regard to features. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Genesis theme framework</a> is immensely popular among WordPress designers and developers for its reliability, functionality, and high standards.</p>\n<p>The theme shop includes all types of WordPress themes: child themes from third-party developers, commercial themes, and more. StudioPress makes sure the quality of all their available themes are top-notch.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress/\" title=\"StudioPress\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">StudioPress</a> was acquired by WP Engine, the world&#8217;s most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/managed-wordpress-hosting-reviews/\" title=\"Best Managed WordPress Hosting Companies (Speed Test)\">managed WordPress hosting</a> company. You&#8217;ll get all StudioPress&#8217; themes for free if you choose <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" title=\"WP Engine\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WP Engine hosting</a> for your website.</p>\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> IsItWP users will also get an additional 20% OFF. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" title=\"WP Engine\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with WP Engine</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> A single theme costs $129, including the Genesis theme framework. If you want to buy all their themes in a bundle, then it costs $499.95.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/elegant-themes/\" title=\"Elegant Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. Elegant Themes</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/elegant-themes/\" title=\"Elegant Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/elegantthemes.jpg\" alt=\"Elegant Themes\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232000\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/elegantthemes.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/elegantthemes-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/elegantthemes-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Elegant Themes is an excellent WordPress theme company. They offer multipurpose WordPress themes built to create a wide variety of websites. Their themes are packed with the Divi Builder, a highly flexible <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">drag and drop builder</a> to design your website pages.</p>\n<p>You can use Elegant Themes Divi theme as a parent theme to many of the Divi child themes. It&#8217;s a powerful theme with hundreds of global content elements, features, and modules.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> For $89, you can get access to all their WordPress themes including 1 year of support and updates. If you want lifetime access to all of their themes and plugins, then it costs $249 (support and updates are also included for life).</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify/\" title=\"Themify\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. Themify</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify/\" title=\"Themify\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themify.jpg\" alt=\"Themify\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232001\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themify.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themify-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themify-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Themify is an well-renowned modern WordPress theme shop with multiple all-purpose themes. Like other popular theme companies, they have their own <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-builder/\" title=\"Themify Builder\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">drag and drop builder</a> to design pages with an ease. The Themify Builder ships with most of the Themify themes.</p>\n<p>All their themes are beautifully crafted with useful features and a simple theme options panel to edit your website. Themify gives you the flexibility to customize everything within a theme.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Single theme (packed with a complementary theme) cost starts from $49. You can get all their themes with lifetime access for $249.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. OceanWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp.jpg\" alt=\"OceanWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232002\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>OceanWP is a WordPress theme company with stylish, free theme demos designed to create any kind of website. From a restaurant site to an online store, they offer multipurpose layouts optimized for SEO and speed performance.</p>\n<p>All OceanWP&#8217;s theme demos are <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"6 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared\">eCommerce-ready</a> and can be integrated with the most popular WordPress services. You can also <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">create a multilingual website</a> with OceanWP themes.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The theme demos are free. You can also use their premium extensions bundle to add powerful features to your theme.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra WordPress Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. Astra WordPress Themes</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra WordPress Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/astra.jpg\" alt=\"Astra\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232003\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/astra.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/astra-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/astra-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Astra is an affordable WordPress theme company offering a theme package with premium starter sites and features. It&#8217;s a stylish, lightweight, and fast performing theme. You can fully customize the theme from the WordPress customizer. It&#8217;s beginner-friendly to set up and built for page builders to create pages easily.</p>\n<p>It comes with pre-built websites for all kinds of business niches. The theme includes beautiful colors, crisp typography, layout options, and more. You can use the Astra WordPress theme to get started in no time.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It has 3 packages and the starting cost is $59 with over 20 starter sites. You can get their complete product bundle, with lifetime access to all their features and updates, for $699.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle/\" title=\"ThemeIsle\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. ThemeIsle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle/\" title=\"ThemeIsle\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themeisle.jpg\" alt=\"ThemeIsle\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232004\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themeisle.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themeisle-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themeisle-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>ThemeIsle is a freemium theme shop with simple and clean WordPress themes. Their free themes are available at WordPress.org, and their paid versions are displayed on their official website. Though the free themes have many features, you&#8217;ll find all the pro options in their paid themes.</p>\n<p>Their theme niches include legal, non-profit, restaurant and food, blogging, and more. These themes are super flexible and easy to set up on your WordPress website.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Single themes cost $89 each. Or, you can get unlimited access to all their themes and plugins for $299.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter/\" title=\"CSSIgniter\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. CSSIgniter</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter/\" title=\"CSSIgniter\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cssigniter.jpg\" alt=\"CSSIgniter\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232005\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cssigniter.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cssigniter-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cssigniter-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>CSSIgniter offers a big collection of multipurpose WordPress themes. Their themes are divided into categories like blogging, magazines, business, news, and hotels. CSSIgniter themes are popular for their flexibility and strength.</p>\n<p>You can use their themes to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create online stores</a>. All their themes are page builder-friendly and support translations.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Single themes cost $49 each. Or, you can get all their themes and resources with a lifetime membership for $249.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom/\" title=\"WPZoom\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. WPZoom</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom/\" title=\"WPZoom\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wpzoom.jpg\" alt=\"WPZoom\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232006\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wpzoom.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wpzoom-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/wpzoom-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WPZoom is another popular WordPress theme company with beautiful themes and templates. They offer magazine, video, portfolio, blogging, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-small-business-website-simple-steps/\" title=\"How to Create a Small Business Website in 5 Simple Steps\">business website</a> themes. They have a powerful built-in framework to add features and design pages.</p>\n<p>The best part is their documentation that helps you get to know each theme&#8217;s features. That way, you can easily decide which theme is best for you.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The starting cost for single theme is $69. You can get all their themes for $99.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes/\" title=\"TeslaThemes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. TeslaThemes</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes/\" title=\"TeslaThemes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/teslathemes.jpg\" alt=\"TeslaThemes\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232007\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/teslathemes.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/teslathemes-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/teslathemes-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>TeslaThemes has a large collection of modern, beautiful WordPress themes. Their themes are eCommerce-ready and can be used for personal blogs, business websites, online stores, etc.</p>\n<p>They focus on styling to attract users with parallax backgrounds, animations, beautiful typography, and colors. You can read their theme documentation to set up and get started.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Single themes cost $58 each. Or, you can get lifetime access to all their themes for $299.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/artisan-themes/\" title=\"Artisan Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Artisan Themes</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/artisan-themes/\" title=\"Artisan Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/artisanthemes.jpg\" alt=\"Artisan Themes\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232008\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/artisanthemes.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/artisanthemes-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/artisanthemes-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Artisan Themes is a well-known WordPress theme shop that offers beautiful all-purpose themes. Their 1-click demo installer helps get your website ready quickly. You can simply replace the demo content with your own to launch your website with ease.</p>\n<p>All their themes are easily integrated with drag and drop page builders. You can use their modular approach to instantly get your website online. They have unlimited designs, pre-built layouts, and more.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> A single theme license costs $129. You can get their All Themes package for $439.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organized-themes/\" title=\"Organized Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">11. Organized Themes</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organized-themes/\" title=\"Organized Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/organizedthemes.jpg\" alt=\"Organized Themes\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232009\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/organizedthemes.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/organizedthemes-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/organizedthemes-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Organized Themes offers beautiful multipurpose WordPress themes. Their themes can be used to create non-profit, church, hotel, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-restaurant-themes/\" title=\"20 Best WordPress Restaurant Themes Compared\">restaurant</a>, business, and blogging sites. You can use the widgetized layouts to design your website pages.</p>\n<p>All themes are fully optimized for speed and performance. The customization is easy with the WordPress live customizer.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Single themes cost $15-$55 depending on the included features. You can get the lifetime access to all their themes for $100.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/graph-paper-press/\" title=\"Graph Paper Press\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">12. Graph Paper Press</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/graph-paper-press/\" title=\"Graph Paper Press\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/graphpaperpress.jpg\" alt=\"Graph Paper Press\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232010\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/graphpaperpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/graphpaperpress-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/graphpaperpress-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Graph Paper Press has an excellent collection of artistically-designed WordPress themes. They offer free and paid themes for photographers, portfolios, business sites, and personal blogs. All themes support eCommerce and can be used to sell your products online.</p>\n<p>Their themes are fully customizable with the WordPress live customizer. Graph Paper Press themes are super flexible and translation-ready.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> They offer an All Themes plan for $99 / year. If you want to purchase lifetime access to all themes, then it&#8217;s a one-time cost of $399.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/churchthemes/\" title=\"ChurchThemes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">13. ChurchThemes</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/churchthemes/\" title=\"ChurchThemes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/churchthemes.jpg\" alt=\"ChurchThemes\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232011\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/churchthemes.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/c