249, you can purchase lifetime access to all their premium themes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/athemes/\" title=\"aThemes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">15. aThemes</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/athemes/\" title=\"aThemes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/athemes.jpg\" alt=\"aThemes\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232013\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/athemes.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/athemes-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/athemes-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>aThemes offers a large collection of beautifully-crafted WordPress themes. Their themes are categorized into portfolio, magazines, news, business, and blog niches.</p>\n<p>All their themes are easy to set up and beginner-friendly. Their theme documentation is strong and up-to-date with the most recent changes.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The starting cost for a single theme is $59. If you want lifetime access to all their themes, then it costs $249.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorilla-themes/\" title=\"Gorilla Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">16. Gorilla Themes</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorilla-themes/\" title=\"Gorilla Themes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/gorillathemes.jpg\" alt=\"Gorilla Themes\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232014\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/gorillathemes.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/gorillathemes-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/gorillathemes-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" />