p.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themetrust.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themetrust-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themetrust-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>ThemeTrust is a premium WordPress theme company with a small collection of stylish themes. Their themes are specifically designed for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-an-online-portfolio/\" title=\"How to Make an Online Portfolio on WordPress (Step by Step)\">portfolio</a>, agency, story-telling, and personal blogs.</p>\n<p>All featured themes have a custom logo, beautiful typography, content-related features, and more. Their themes are easy to set up and can be customized using the live WordPress customizer.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Single themes cost $58.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeskingdom/\" title=\"Themes Kingdom\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">32. Themes Kingdom</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeskingdom/\" title=\"Themes Kingdom\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themeskingdom.jpg\" alt=\"Themes Kingdom\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231997\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themeskingdom.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themeskingdom-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themeskingdom-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Themes Kingdom is a WordPress theme shop for multipurpose themes. Their themes have features for portfolio, creative sites, and blogs. All their themes are fully responsive and offer custom backgrounds to get the results you need.</p>\n<p>Additionally, their themes have beautifully crisp typography, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-image-optimization-plugins-wordpress/\" title=\"6 Best Image Optimization Plugins for WordPress (Compared)\">image optimization</a>, and more. All themes are easy to set up and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"6 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared\">eCommerce-ready</a> to sell your products online.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The starting cost for a single theme is $59 / year. You can get the access to their All Themes membership for $89 / year.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themestop/\" title=\"ThemeStop\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">33. ThemeStop</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themestop/\" title=\"ThemeStop\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themestop.jpg\" alt=\"ThemeStop\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231998\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themestop.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themestop-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/themestop-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>ThemeStop offers a unique collection of stylish, colorful WordPress themes. Their themes are categorized into photography, creative, blogs, magazines, travel, and business niches.</p>\n<p>They have <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins\">social media integration</a>, Adsense optimization, eCommerce support, and are translation-ready to create multilingual sites. The theme set up is simple and easy.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress theme shops to buy your perfect theme. You may also like our list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/free-web-hosting/\" title=\"11 Best Free Web Hosting Services [Host at $0 Cost]\">best free web hosting services</a>.</p>\n<p>T